@startuml
[*] --> CreateAccount: The system shall allow a user to create an account.
CreateAccount --> Login: The system shall allow a user to log in to their existing account.
Login --> CheckWeather: The system shall allow a user to check the weather for their current location or another location after logging in.
CheckWeather --> ValidateLocation: The system shall end the process if a new location entered is not valid.
ValidateLocation --> ShowWeatherInfo: The system shall allow a user to choose what to check (temperature, humidity, rainfall, pressure, or dew point) if the entered location is valid.
ShowWeatherInfo --> UpdateWeatherInfo: The system shall update and show the selected weather information to the user.
UpdateWeatherInfo --> ViewAdditionalDetails: The system shall allow a user to view additional weather details (alerts, a weekly analysis, a future prediction, or a graph).
ViewAdditionalDetails --> Logout: The system shall end the session when the user logs out.
Logout --> EndProcess: The system shall end the process if the registration is not successful.

@enduml
